{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":928,"text":"So I'm here to tell you\nthat we have a problem with boys,"},{"time":4123,"text":"and it's a serious problem with boys."},{"time":6757,"text":"Their culture isn't working in schools,"},{"time":9409,"text":"and I'm going to share with you ways"},{"time":11211,"text":"that we can think\nabout overcoming that problem."},{"time":14305,"text":"First, I want to start\nby saying, this is a boy,"},{"time":17295,"text":"and this is a girl,"},{"time":19841,"text":"and this is probably stereotypically\nwhat you think of as a boy and a girl."},{"time":23413,"text":"If I essentialize gender for you today,\nthen you can dismiss what I have to say."},{"time":27220,"text":"So I'm not going to do that,\nI'm not interested in doing that."},{"time":30208,"text":"This is a different kind of boy\nand a different kind of girl."},{"time":33449,"text":"So the point here is that not all boys\nexist within these rigid boundaries"},{"time":37906,"text":"of what we think of as boys and girls,"},{"time":40120,"text":"and not all girls exist\nwithin those rigid boundaries"},{"time":42699,"text":"of what we think of as girls."},{"time":44115,"text":"But, in fact, most boys\ntend to be a certain way,"},{"time":47864,"text":"and most girls tend to be a certain way."},{"time":49865,"text":"And the point is that, for boys,"},{"time":52128,"text":"the way that they exist\nand the culture that they embrace"},{"time":55338,"text":"isn't working well in schools now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":57870,"text":"How do we know that?"},{"time":59118,"text":"The 100 girls project\ntells us some really nice statistics."},{"time":63901,"text":"For example, for every 100 girls\nthat are suspended from school,"},{"time":67438,"text":"there are 250 boys\nthat are suspended from school."},{"time":70382,"text":"For every 100 girls\nwho are expelled from school,"},{"time":72729,"text":"there are 335 boys\nwho are expelled from school."},{"time":76080,"text":"For every 100 girls in special education,"},{"time":78451,"text":"there are 217 boys."},{"time":80642,"text":"For every 100 girls\nwith a learning disability,"},{"time":82867,"text":"there are 276 boys."},{"time":85285,"text":"For every 100 girls\nwith an emotional disturbance diagnosed,"},{"time":89771,"text":"we have 324 boys."},{"time":91565,"text":"And by the way, all of these numbers\nare significantly higher"},{"time":95165,"text":"if you happen to be black,"},{"time":96609,"text":"if you happen to be poor,"},{"time":98476,"text":"if you happen to exist\nin an overcrowded school."},{"time":102249,"text":"And if you are a boy,"},{"time":104394,"text":"you're four times as likely\nto be diagnosed with ADHD --"},{"time":108154,"text":"Attention Deficit Hyperactivity Disorder."}]},{"cues":[{"time":111079,"text":"Now there is another side to this."},{"time":114164,"text":"And it is important that we recognize\nthat women still need help in school,"},{"time":119798,"text":"that salaries are still\nsignificantly lower,"},{"time":122085,"text":"even when controlled for job types,"},{"time":124407,"text":"and that girls have continued to struggle\nin math and science for years."},{"time":128714,"text":"That's all true."},{"time":129894,"text":"Nothing about that prevents us"},{"time":132197,"text":"from paying attention\nto the literacy needs"},{"time":134255,"text":"of our boys between ages three and 13."},{"time":136849,"text":"And so we should."},{"time":138025,"text":"In fact, what we ought to do\nis take a page from their playbook,"},{"time":141072,"text":"because the initiatives and programs\nthat have been set in place"},{"time":145343,"text":"for women in science and engineering\nand mathematics are fantastic."},{"time":149208,"text":"They've done a lot of good\nfor girls in these situations,"},{"time":153162,"text":"and we ought to be thinking about\nhow we can make that happen for boys too"},{"time":157000,"text":"in their younger years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":159100,"text":"Even in their older years,"},{"time":161000,"text":"what we find is that\nthere's still a problem."},{"time":163511,"text":"When we look at the universities,"},{"time":165120,"text":"60 percent of baccalaureate degrees\nare going to women now,"},{"time":168142,"text":"which is a significant shift."},{"time":170000,"text":"And in fact, university administrators\nare a little uncomfortable about the idea"},{"time":173895,"text":"that we may be getting close to 70 percent\nfemale population in universities."},{"time":178824,"text":"This makes university\nadministrators very nervous,"},{"time":181198,"text":"because girls don't want to go\nto schools that don't have boys."},{"time":186530,"text":"And so we're starting to see"},{"time":188652,"text":"the establishment of men centers\nand men studies"},{"time":191833,"text":"to think about how do we engage men\nin their experiences in the university."},{"time":196134,"text":"If you talk to faculty,\nthey may say, \"Ugh. Yeah, well,"},{"time":198935,"text":"they're playing video games,"},{"time":200507,"text":"and they're gambling\nonline all night long,"},{"time":203500,"text":"and they're playing World of Warcraft,"},{"time":205339,"text":"and that's affecting\ntheir academic achievement.\""},{"time":210460,"text":"Guess what?"},{"time":211665,"text":"Video games are not the cause."},{"time":214160,"text":"Video games are a symptom."},{"time":216481,"text":"They were turned off a long time\nbefore they got here."}]},{"cues":[{"time":221127,"text":"So let's talk about\nwhy they got turned off"},{"time":223810,"text":"when they were between the ages\nof three and 13."},{"time":227190,"text":"There are three reasons that I believe"},{"time":229093,"text":"that boys are out of sync\nwith the culture of schools today."},{"time":232754,"text":"The first is zero tolerance."},{"time":235367,"text":"A kindergarten teacher I know,\nher son donated all of his toys to her,"},{"time":240408,"text":"and when he did, she had to go through\nand pull out all the little plastic guns."},{"time":247000,"text":"You can't have plastic knives\nand swords and axes"},{"time":249518,"text":"and all that kind of thing\nin a kindergarten classroom."},{"time":252685,"text":"What is it that we're afraid that this\nyoung man is going to do with this gun?"},{"time":256584,"text":"I mean, really."},{"time":258658,"text":"But here he stands as testament"},{"time":261000,"text":"to the fact that you can't roughhouse\non the playground today."},{"time":264300,"text":"Now I'm not advocating for bullies."},{"time":266333,"text":"I'm not suggesting that we need to be\nallowing guns and knives in the school."},{"time":271560,"text":"But when we say that an Eagle Scout\nin a high school classroom"},{"time":275840,"text":"who has a locked parked car\nin the parking lot and a penknife in it,"},{"time":279189,"text":"has to be suspended from school,"},{"time":281236,"text":"I think we may have gone\na little too far with zero tolerance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":284560,"text":"Another way that zero tolerance\nlives itself out"},{"time":286912,"text":"is in the writing of boys."},{"time":288227,"text":"In a lot of classrooms today,"},{"time":289636,"text":"you're not allowed to write\nabout anything that's violent."},{"time":292380,"text":"You're not allowed to write about anything\nthat has to do with video games."},{"time":295930,"text":"These topics are banned."},{"time":297124,"text":"Boy comes home from school, and he says,"},{"time":299096,"text":"\"I hate writing.\""},{"time":300570,"text":"\"Why do you hate writing, son?\nWhat's wrong with writing?\""},{"time":303321,"text":"\"Now I have to write\nwhat she tells me to write.\""},{"time":305658,"text":"\"OK, what is she telling you to write?\""},{"time":308103,"text":"\"Poems. I have to write poems."},{"time":310488,"text":"And little moments in my life."},{"time":312508,"text":"I don't want to write that stuff.\""},{"time":314880,"text":"\"Well, what do you want to write?"},{"time":316546,"text":"What do you want to write about?\""},{"time":318161,"text":"\"I want to write about video games.\nI want to write about leveling-up."},{"time":321474,"text":"I want to write about\nthis really interesting world."},{"time":323936,"text":"I want to write about a tornado\nthat comes into our house"},{"time":326789,"text":"and blows all the windows out,"},{"time":328325,"text":"and ruins all the furniture\nand kills everybody.\""},{"time":330655,"text":"\"All right. OK.\""},{"time":332150,"text":"You tell a teacher that,\nand they'll ask you, in all seriousness,"},{"time":335897,"text":"\"Should we send this child\nto the psychologist?\""},{"time":339617,"text":"And the answer is no, he's just a boy."},{"time":342512,"text":"He's just a little boy."},{"time":345176,"text":"It's not OK to write these kinds of things\nin classrooms today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":349834,"text":"So that's the first reason:"},{"time":351153,"text":"Zero tolerance policies\nand the way they're lived out."},{"time":353726,"text":"The next reason that boys' cultures\nare out of sync with school cultures:"},{"time":357231,"text":"there are fewer male teachers."},{"time":358692,"text":"Anybody who's over 15\ndoesn't know what this means,"},{"time":361475,"text":"because in the last 10 years,"},{"time":363255,"text":"the number of elementary school\nclassroom teachers has been cut in half."},{"time":367072,"text":"We went from 14 percent to seven percent."},{"time":370940,"text":"That means that 93 percent of the teachers"},{"time":373287,"text":"that our young men get in elementary\nclassrooms are women."},{"time":377483,"text":"Now what's the problem with this?"},{"time":379737,"text":"Women are great, yep, absolutely."},{"time":382340,"text":"But male role models for boys\nthat say it's all right to be smart --"},{"time":386806,"text":"they've got dads, they've got pastors,\nthey've got Cub Scout leaders,"},{"time":390432,"text":"but ultimately, six hours a day,\nfive days a week"},{"time":393540,"text":"they're spending in a classroom,"},{"time":395810,"text":"and most of those classrooms\nare not places where men exist."},{"time":399198,"text":"And so they say, I guess this really\nisn't a place for boys."},{"time":403123,"text":"This is a place for girls."},{"time":404815,"text":"And I'm not very good at this,"},{"time":406429,"text":"so I guess I'd better go play video games"},{"time":409661,"text":"or get into sports,\nor something like that,"},{"time":411696,"text":"because I obviously don't belong here."},{"time":413602,"text":"Men don't belong here,\nthat's pretty obvious."}]},{"cues":[{"time":415736,"text":"So that may be a very direct way\nthat we see it happen."},{"time":420072,"text":"But less directly, the lack of male\npresence in the culture --"},{"time":424497,"text":"you've got a teachers' lounge,\nand they're having a conversation"},{"time":427711,"text":"about Joey and Johnny\nwho beat each other up on the playground."},{"time":431862,"text":"\"What are we going to do with these boys?\""},{"time":433890,"text":"The answer to that question changes"},{"time":435598,"text":"depending on who's sitting\naround that table."},{"time":437723,"text":"Are there men around that table?"},{"time":439307,"text":"Are there moms who've raised boys\naround that table?"},{"time":441781,"text":"You'll see, the conversation changes"},{"time":443547,"text":"depending upon who's sitting\naround the table."}]},{"cues":[{"time":445719,"text":"Third reason that boys\nare out of sync with school today:"},{"time":448595,"text":"Kindergarten is the old\nsecond grade, folks."},{"time":451063,"text":"We have a serious compression\nof the curriculum happening out there."},{"time":455332,"text":"When you're three, you better be able\nto write your name legibly,"},{"time":458449,"text":"or else we'll consider it\na developmental delay."},{"time":461494,"text":"By the time you're in first grade,"},{"time":463161,"text":"you should be able to read\nparagraphs of text"},{"time":465790,"text":"with maybe a picture, maybe not,\nin a book of maybe 25 to 30 pages."},{"time":469294,"text":"If you don't,"},{"time":470498,"text":"we're probably going to be putting you\ninto a Title I special reading program."},{"time":474197,"text":"And if you ask Title I teachers,\nthey'll tell you"},{"time":476519,"text":"they've got about four or five boys\nfor every girl that's in their program,"},{"time":480162,"text":"in the elementary grades."}]},{"cues":[{"time":481390,"text":"The reason that this is a problem"},{"time":483168,"text":"is because the message\nthat boys are getting"},{"time":486245,"text":"is, \"You need to do what the teacher\nasks you to do all the time.\""},{"time":491092,"text":"The teacher's salary depends\non \"No Child Left Behind\""},{"time":495276,"text":"and \"Race to the Top\"\nand accountability and testing"},{"time":498000,"text":"and all of this."},{"time":500000,"text":"So she has to figure out a way\nto get all these boys"},{"time":503998,"text":"through this curriculum -- and girls."},{"time":507882,"text":"This compressed curriculum is bad\nfor all active kids."},{"time":512486,"text":"And what happens is,"},{"time":514330,"text":"she says, \"Please, sit down,\nbe quiet, do what you're told,"},{"time":519014,"text":"follow the rules, manage your time,\nfocus, be a girl.\""},{"time":525309,"text":"That's what she tells them."},{"time":526891,"text":"Indirectly, that's what she tells them."},{"time":529000,"text":"And so this is a very serious problem."},{"time":531084,"text":"Where is it coming from?\nIt's coming from us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":533465,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":536732,"text":"We want our babies to read\nwhen they are six months old."},{"time":539724,"text":"Have you seen the ads?"},{"time":541000,"text":"We want to live in Lake Wobegon\nwhere every child is above average ..."},{"time":546398,"text":"but what this does to our children\nis really not healthy."},{"time":549866,"text":"It's not developmentally appropriate,"},{"time":551700,"text":"and it's particularly bad for boys."}]},{"cues":[{"time":554144,"text":"So what do we do?"},{"time":555900,"text":"We need to meet them where they are."},{"time":557649,"text":"We need to put ourselves into boy culture."},{"time":559937,"text":"We need to change the mindset\nof acceptance in boys"},{"time":565216,"text":"in elementary schools."},{"time":567168,"text":"More specifically, we can do\nsome very specific things."},{"time":570388,"text":"We can design better games."},{"time":572000,"text":"Most of the educational games\nthat are out there today"},{"time":574839,"text":"are really flashcards."},{"time":576388,"text":"They're glorified drill and practice."},{"time":578354,"text":"They don't have the depth,\nthe rich narrative"},{"time":581191,"text":"that really engaging video games have,"},{"time":583967,"text":"that the boys are really interested in."},{"time":585994,"text":"So we need to design better games."},{"time":587660,"text":"We need to talk to teachers and parents\nand school board members and politicians."},{"time":591510,"text":"We need to make sure that people see\nthat we need more men in the classroom."},{"time":595110,"text":"We need to look carefully\nat our zero tolerance policies."},{"time":597828,"text":"Do they make sense?"},{"time":599020,"text":"We need to think about how to uncompress\nthis curriculum if we can,"},{"time":603000,"text":"trying to bring boys back into a space\nthat is comfortable for them."},{"time":607000,"text":"All of those conversations\nneed to be happening."}]},{"cues":[{"time":609310,"text":"There are some great examples\nout there of schools --"},{"time":612137,"text":"the New York Times\njust talked about a school recently."},{"time":615644,"text":"A game designer from the New School"},{"time":618000,"text":"put together a wonderful\nvideo gaming school."},{"time":621392,"text":"But it only treats a few kids,\nand so this isn't very scalable."},{"time":626253,"text":"We have to change the culture\nand the feelings"},{"time":628433,"text":"that politicians and school board\nmembers and parents have"},{"time":633279,"text":"about the way we accept\nand what we accept in our schools today."},{"time":636370,"text":"We need to find more money\nfor game design."},{"time":638403,"text":"Because good games,\nreally good games, cost money,"},{"time":640781,"text":"and World of Warcraft has quite a budget."},{"time":642792,"text":"Most of the educational games do not."}]},{"cues":[{"time":644908,"text":"Where we started:"},{"time":646180,"text":"my colleagues Mike Petner,\nShawn Vashaw, myself,"},{"time":649000,"text":"we started by trying to look\nat the teachers' attitudes"},{"time":651615,"text":"and find out how do they really\nfeel about gaming,"},{"time":653984,"text":"what do they say about it."},{"time":655268,"text":"And we discovered that they talk\nabout the kids in their school,"},{"time":660266,"text":"who talk about gaming,\nin pretty demeaning ways."},{"time":663532,"text":"They say, \"Oh, yeah. They're always\ntalking about that stuff."},{"time":666749,"text":"They're talking\nabout their little action figures"},{"time":669097,"text":"and their little achievements\nor merit badges,"},{"time":671509,"text":"or whatever it is that they get."},{"time":673591,"text":"And they're always talking\nabout this stuff.\""},{"time":675717,"text":"And they say these things as if it's OK."},{"time":677698,"text":"But if it were your culture,\nthink of how that might feel."},{"time":681000,"text":"It's very uncomfortable\nto be on the receiving end"},{"time":683405,"text":"of that kind of language."},{"time":685976,"text":"They're nervous about anything\nthat has anything to do with violence"},{"time":689216,"text":"because of the zero tolerance policies."},{"time":691125,"text":"They are sure that parents\nand administrators"},{"time":693260,"text":"will never accept anything."}]},{"cues":[{"time":694582,"text":"So we really need to think\nabout looking at teacher attitudes"},{"time":697490,"text":"and finding ways to change the attitudes,"},{"time":700276,"text":"so that teachers are much more open\nand accepting of boy cultures"},{"time":704270,"text":"in their classrooms."},{"time":705484,"text":"Because, ultimately, if we don't,"},{"time":707576,"text":"then we're going to have boys\nwho leave elementary school saying,"},{"time":710872,"text":"\"Well I guess that was just\na place for girls, it wasn't for me."},{"time":713924,"text":"So I've got to do gaming,\nor I've got to do sports.\""},{"time":717156,"text":"If we change these things,\nif we pay attention to these things,"},{"time":720193,"text":"and we reengage boys in their learning,"},{"time":722136,"text":"they will leave the elementary\nschools saying, \"I'm smart.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":726134,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":727309,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}